PRIVACY STATEMENT
1. General
Tally Weijl Trading AG and the companies belonging to the Tally Weijl Holding AG Group (hereinafter referred to as “we” or “Tally Weijl”) attach great importance to protecting your privacy when you use our websites and the Tally Weijl online store. For this reason, we have created the following privacy statement to explain what personal data and other information Tally Weijl processes.
Please note that persons under the age of 16 may not transfer personal information to us without the consent of their legal guardian and may not declare consent on their own behalf. All changes to our privacy statement will be published on this website and, if necessary, users will be notified via email.
The controller is
Tally Weijl Trading AG,
Viaduktstrasse 42,
4051 Basel, Switzerland
Unique Business Identification Number CHE-104.296.780
Chair of the Board of Directors: Beat Grüring.
Tally Weijl Trading AG is also the operator of this website and the online shop.
2. Contact us
Do you have questions or comments concerning data protection at Tally Weijl? Please contact our data protection officer. The easiest and fastest way to contact us is via email:
privacy@tally-weijl.com
Tally Weijl Trading AG,
Privacy, Legal Service
Viaduktstrasse 42
4051 Basel, Switzerland
Our representative within the EU is Tally Weijl Retail Germany GmbH:
